{"doc":{"isMarkdown":false,"isTranslated":true,"isActive":true,"flaws":{},"title":"Object.is()","mdn_url":"/pt-BR/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Object/is","locale":"pt-BR","native":"Português (do Brasil)","sidebarHTML":"<ol><li><strong><a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects\">Standard built-in objects</a></strong></li><li><strong><a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Object\"><code>Object</code></a></strong></li><li data-default-state=\"open\"><a href=\"#\"><strong>Propriedades</strong></a><ol><li><a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Object/constructor\"><code>Object.prototype.constructor</code></a></li><li><svg class=\"icon icon-deprecated\" tabindex=\"0\">\n    <use xlink:href=\"/assets/badges.svg#icon-deprecated\"></use>\n</svg><a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Object/proto\"><code>Object.prototype.__proto__</code></a></li></ol></li><li data-default-state=\"open\"><a href=\"#\"><strong>Métodos</strong></a><ol><li><svg class=\"icon icon-deprecated\" tabindex=\"0\">\n    <use xlink:href=\"/assets/badges.svg#icon-deprecated\"></use>\n</svg><a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Object/__defineGetter__\"><code>Object.prototype.__defineGetter__()</code></a></li><li><svg class=\"icon icon-deprecated\" tabindex=\"0\">\n    <use xlink:href=\"/assets/badges.svg#icon-deprecated\"></use>\n</svg><a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Object/__defineSetter__\"><code>Object.prototype.__defineSetter__()</code></a></li><li><svg class=\"icon icon-deprecated\" tabindex=\"0\">\n    <use xlink:href=\"/assets/badges.svg#icon-deprecated\"></use>\n</svg><a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Object/__lookupGetter__\"><code>Object.prototype.__lookupGetter__()</code></a></li><li><svg class=\"icon icon-deprecated\" tabindex=\"0\">\n    <use xlink:href=\"/assets/badges.svg#icon-deprecated\"></use>\n</svg><a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Object/__lookupSetter__\"><code>Object.prototype.__lookupSetter__()</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Object/assign\"><code>Object.assign()</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Object/create\"><code>Object.create()</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Object/defineProperties\"><code>Object.defineProperties()</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Object/defineProperty\"><code>Object.defineProperty()</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Object/entries\"><code>Object.entries()</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Object/freeze\"><code>Object.freeze()</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Object/fromEntries\"><code>Object.fromEntries()</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Object/getOwnPropertyDescriptor\"><code>Object.getOwnPropertyDescriptor()</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Object/getOwnPropertyDescriptors\"><code>Object.getOwnPropertyDescriptors()</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Object/getOwnPropertyNames\"><code>Object.getOwnPropertyNames()</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Object/getOwnPropertySymbols\"><code>Object.getOwnPropertySymbols()</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Object/getPrototypeOf\"><code>Object.getPrototypeOf()</code></a></li><li><svg class=\"icon icon-experimental\" tabindex=\"0\">\n    <use xlink:href=\"/assets/badges.svg#icon-experimental\"></use>\n</svg><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Object/hasOwn\"><code>Object.hasOwn()</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Object/hasOwnProperty\"><code>Object.prototype.hasOwnProperty()</code></a></li><li><em><code>Object.is()</code></em></li><li><a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Object/isExtensible\"><code>Object.isExtensible()</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Object/isFrozen\"><code>Object.isFrozen()</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Object/isPrototypeOf\"><code>Object.prototype.isPrototypeOf()</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Object/isSealed\"><code>Object.isSealed()</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Object/keys\"><code>Object.keys()</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Object/preventExtensions\"><code>Object.preventExtensions()</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Object/propertyIsEnumerable\"><code>Object.prototype.propertyIsEnumerable()</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Object/seal\"><code>Object.seal()</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Object/setPrototypeOf\"><code>Object.setPrototypeOf()</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Object/toLocaleString\"><code>Object.prototype.toLocaleString()</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Object/toString\"><code>Object.prototype.toString()</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Object/valueOf\"><code>Object.prototype.valueOf()</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Object/values\"><code>Object.values()</code></a></li></ol></li></ol>","body":[{"type":"prose","value":{"id":null,"title":null,"isH3":false,"content":"<div id=\"sect1\"></div>\n\n<p>O método&nbsp;<code><strong>Object.is()</strong></code>&nbsp;determina se dois valores correspondem <a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/JavaScript/Equality_comparisons_and_sameness\">ao mesmo valor</a>.</p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"sintaxe","title":"Sintaxe","isH3":false,"content":"<pre class=\"syntaxbox notranslate\"><code>Object.is(<var>value1</var>, <var>value2</var>);</code></pre>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"parâmetros","title":"Parâmetros","isH3":true,"content":"<dl>\n <dt id=\"value1\"><code>value1</code></dt>\n <dd>O primeiro valor a ser comparado.</dd>\n <dt id=\"value2\"><code>value2</code></dt>\n <dd>O segundo valor a ser comparado.</dd>\n</dl>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"return_value","title":"Return value","isH3":true,"content":"<p>Um <a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Boolean\"><code>Boolean</code></a> indicando se os dois argumentos possuem o mesmo valor ou não.</p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"descrição","title":"Descrição","isH3":false,"content":"<p><code>Object.is()</code>&nbsp;determina se dois valores correspondem <a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/JavaScript/Equality_comparisons_and_sameness\">ao mesmo valor</a>.&nbsp;Dois valores&nbsp;correspondem ao mesmo valor se uma das seguintes condições for verdadeira:</p>\n\n<ul>\n <li>ambos&nbsp;são&nbsp;<a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/undefined\"><code>undefined</code></a></li>\n <li>ambos são&nbsp;<a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Operators/null\"><code>null</code></a></li>\n <li>ambos são&nbsp;<code>true</code>&nbsp;ou ambos são&nbsp;<code>false</code></li>\n <li>ambos são strings do mesmo comprimento,&nbsp;com os mesmos&nbsp;caracteres</li>\n <li>ambos são o mesmo objeto</li>\n <li>ambos são numéricos e\n  <ul>\n   <li>ambos são&nbsp;<code>+0</code></li>\n   <li>ambos são&nbsp;<code>-0</code></li>\n   <li>ambos são <a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/NaN\"><code>NaN</code></a></li>\n   <li>ou ambos são não-zero e ambos são não&nbsp;<a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/NaN\"><code>NaN</code></a> e ambos&nbsp;correspondem ao mesmo valor</li>\n  </ul>\n </li>\n</ul>\n\n<p>Isso <em>não é&nbsp;</em>o mesmo que ser igual de acordo com o operador <a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Operators\"><code>==</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a>. O operador&nbsp;<a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Operators\"><code>==</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a> aplica diversas coerções para ambos os lados (se eles não correspondem ao mesmo Tipo) antes de testar a igualdade (resultando em comportamentos como a comparação&nbsp;<code>\"\" == false&nbsp;</code>retornar&nbsp;<code>true</code>), enquanto&nbsp;<code>Object.is</code>&nbsp;não realiza a coerção de nenhum dos valores.</p>\n\n<p>Isso também&nbsp;<em>não</em>&nbsp;<em>é</em> o mesmo que ser igual de acordo com o operador&nbsp;<a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Operators\"><code>===</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a>. O operador&nbsp;<a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Operators\"><code>===</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a> (assim como o operador&nbsp;<a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Operators\"><code>==</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a>) trata os valores numéricos&nbsp;<code>-0</code>&nbsp;e&nbsp;<code>+0</code>&nbsp;como iguais e trata&nbsp;<a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Number/NaN\"><code>Number.NaN</code></a>&nbsp;como não igual a&nbsp;<a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/NaN\"><code>NaN</code></a>.</p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"exemplos","title":"Exemplos","isH3":false,"content":"<div class=\"code-example\"><pre class=\"brush: js notranslate\"><code>Object<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">is</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string\">'foo'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token string\">'foo'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>     <span class=\"token comment\">// true</span>\nObject<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">is</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>window<span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> window<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>   <span class=\"token comment\">// true</span>\n\nObject<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">is</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string\">'foo'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token string\">'bar'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>     <span class=\"token comment\">// false</span>\nObject<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">is</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">[</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">]</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">[</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">]</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>           <span class=\"token comment\">// false</span>\n\n<span class=\"token keyword\">var</span> test <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span> <span class=\"token literal-property property\">a</span><span class=\"token operator\">:</span> <span class=\"token number\">1</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\nObject<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">is</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>test<span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> test<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>       <span class=\"token comment\">// true</span>\n\nObject<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">is</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token keyword\">null</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">null</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>       <span class=\"token comment\">// true</span>\n\n<span class=\"token comment\">// Casos especiais</span>\nObject<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">is</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token number\">0</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token operator\">-</span><span class=\"token number\">0</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>            <span class=\"token comment\">// false</span>\nObject<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">is</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token operator\">-</span><span class=\"token number\">0</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token operator\">-</span><span class=\"token number\">0</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>           <span class=\"token comment\">// true</span>\nObject<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">is</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token number\">NaN</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token number\">0</span><span class=\"token operator\">/</span><span class=\"token number\">0</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>         <span class=\"token comment\">// true</span>\n</code></pre></div>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"polyfill_para_navegadores_que_não_suportam_es6","title":"Polyfill para navegadores que não suportam&nbsp;ES6","isH3":false,"content":"<p><code>Object.is()</code>&nbsp;é uma adição proposta ao padrão ECMA-262; e como tal, pode não estar presente em todos os navegadores. Você pode contornar essa situação por meio da adição&nbsp;do seguinte código no começo de seus scripts.&nbsp;Isso permitirá a você utilizar&nbsp;<code>Object.is()</code>, mesmo quando não houver suporte por parte do navegador.</p>\n\n<div class=\"code-example\"><pre class=\"brush: js notranslate\"><code><span class=\"token keyword\">if</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token operator\">!</span>Object<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>is<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n  Object<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function-variable function\">is</span> <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">function</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token parameter\">x<span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> y</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n    <span class=\"token comment\">// Algoritmo para verificar se os valores sao iguais</span>\n    <span class=\"token keyword\">if</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>x <span class=\"token operator\">===</span> y<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span> <span class=\"token comment\">// Passos 1-5, 7-10</span>\n      <span class=\"token comment\">// Passos 6.b-6.e: +0 != -0</span>\n      <span class=\"token keyword\">return</span> x <span class=\"token operator\">!==</span> <span class=\"token number\">0</span> <span class=\"token operator\">||</span> <span class=\"token number\">1</span> <span class=\"token operator\">/</span> x <span class=\"token operator\">===</span> <span class=\"token number\">1</span> <span class=\"token operator\">/</span> y<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n    <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">else</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n      <span class=\"token comment\">// Passo 6.a: NaN == NaN</span>\n      <span class=\"token keyword\">return</span> x <span class=\"token operator\">!==</span> x <span class=\"token operator\">&amp;&amp;</span> y <span class=\"token operator\">!==</span> y<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n    <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n  <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n</code></pre></div>","titleAsText":"Polyfill para navegadores que não suportam ES6"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"especificações","title":"Especificações","isH3":false,"content":"<table class=\"standard-table\">\n <tbody>\n  <tr>\n   <th scope=\"col\">Especificação</th>\n   <th scope=\"col\">Status</th>\n   <th scope=\"col\">Comentário</th>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n   <td><a href=\"https://www.ecma-international.org/ecma-262/6.0/#sec-object.is\" hreflang=\"en\" lang=\"en\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">ECMAScript 2015 (6th Edition, ECMA-262)<br><small lang=\"pt-BR\">The definition of 'Object.is' in that specification.</small></a></td>\n   <td><span class=\"spec-standard\">Padrão</span></td>\n   <td>Definição inicial.</td>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n   <td><a href=\"https://tc39.es/ecma262/#sec-object.is\" hreflang=\"en\" lang=\"en\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">ECMAScript (ECMA-262)<br><small lang=\"pt-BR\">The definition of 'Object.is' in that specification.</small></a></td>\n   <td><span class=\"spec-living\">Padrão em tempo real</span></td>\n   <td>&nbsp;</td>\n  </tr>\n </tbody>\n</table>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"browser_compatibility","title":"Compatibilidade com navegadores","isH3":false,"content":"<div id=\"sect2\"><div class=\"notecard note\" id=\"sect3\"><strong><a href=\"https://github.com/mdn/browser-compat-data\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">Estamos convertendo nossos dados de compatibilidade para o formato JSON</a></strong>.\n            Esta tabela de compatibilidade ainda usa o formato antigo,\n            pois ainda não convertemos os dados que ela contém.\n            <strong><a href=\"/en-US/docs/MDN/Structures/Compatibility_tables\" class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\">Descubra como você pode ajudar! (en-US)</a></strong></div>\n\n<div class=\"htab\" id=\"sect4\">\n    <a id=\"AutoCompatibilityTable\" name=\"AutoCompatibilityTable\"></a>\n    <ul>\n        <li class=\"selected\"><a href=\"#compat-desktop\">Desktop</a></li>\n        <li><a href=\"#compat-mobile\">Dispositivo móvel</a></li>\n    </ul>\n</div></div>\n\n<div id=\"compat-desktop\">\n<table class=\"compat-table\">\n <tbody>\n  <tr>\n   <th>Recurso</th>\n   <th>Chrome</th>\n   <th>Firefox (Gecko)</th>\n   <th>Internet Explorer</th>\n   <th>Opera</th>\n   <th>Safari</th>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n   <td>Suporte básico</td>\n   <td>30</td>\n   <td><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Mozilla/Firefox/Releases/22\" title=\"Released on 2013-06-25.\">22</a> (22)</td>\n   <td>\n    <p><span style=\"color:#f00;\">Não suportado</span></p>\n   </td>\n   <td><span style=\"color: #888\" title=\"Please update this with the earliest version of support.\">(Yes)</span></td>\n   <td>9</td>\n  </tr>\n </tbody>\n</table>\n</div>\n\n<div id=\"compat-mobile\">\n<table class=\"compat-table\">\n <tbody>\n  <tr>\n   <th>Recurso</th>\n   <th>Android</th>\n   <th>Chrome for Android</th>\n   <th>Firefox Mobile (Gecko)</th>\n   <th>IE Mobile</th>\n   <th>Opera Mobile</th>\n   <th>Safari Mobile</th>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n   <td>Suporte básico</td>\n   <td><span style=\"color:#f00;\">Não suportado</span></td>\n   <td><span title=\"Compatibility unknown; please update this.\" style=\"color: rgb(255, 153, 0);\">?</span></td>\n   <td>22.0 (22)</td>\n   <td><span style=\"color:#f00;\">Não suportado</span></td>\n   <td><span style=\"color:#f00;\">Não suportado</span></td>\n   <td>9</td>\n  </tr>\n </tbody>\n</table>\n</div>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"veja_também","title":"Veja também","isH3":false,"content":"<ul>\n <li><a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/JavaScript/Equality_comparisons_and_sameness\">Comparações de igualdade</a>&nbsp;— uma comparação dos três recursos implementados para verificação&nbsp;de igualdade.</li>\n</ul>"}}],"toc":[{"text":"Sintaxe","id":"sintaxe"},{"text":"Descrição","id":"descrição"},{"text":"Exemplos","id":"exemplos"},{"text":"Polyfill para navegadores que não suportam&nbsp;ES6","id":"polyfill_para_navegadores_que_não_suportam_es6"},{"text":"Especificações","id":"especificações"},{"text":"Compatibilidade com navegadores","id":"browser_compatibility"},{"text":"Veja também","id":"veja_também"}],"summary":"O método Object.is() determina se dois valores correspondem ao mesmo valor.","popularity":0.0004,"modified":"2022-07-19T02:29:32.000Z","other_translations":[{"title":"Object.is()","locale":"de","native":"Deutsch"},{"title":"Object.is()","locale":"en-US","native":"English (US)"},{"title":"Object.is()","locale":"es","native":"Español"},{"title":"Object.is()","locale":"fr","native":"Français"},{"title":"Object.is()","locale":"ja","native":"日本語"},{"title":"Object.is()","locale":"ko","native":"한국어"},{"title":"Object.is()","locale":"ru","native":"Русский"},{"title":"Object.is()","locale":"zh-CN","native":"中文 (简体)"}],"source":{"folder":"pt-br/web/javascript/reference/global_objects/object/is","github_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/blob/main/files/pt-br/web/javascript/reference/global_objects/object/is/index.html","last_commit_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/commit/5fe4ab11259b37914fab41914e84897fea47d143","filename":"index.html"},"parents":[{"uri":"/pt-BR/docs/Web","title":"Tecnologia Web para desenvolvedores"},{"uri":"/pt-BR/docs/Web/JavaScript","title":"JavaScript"},{"uri":"/pt-BR/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference","title":"Referência JavaScript"},{"uri":"/pt-BR/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects","title":"Objetos Globais"},{"uri":"/pt-BR/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Object","title":"Object"},{"uri":"/pt-BR/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Object/is","title":"Object.is()"}],"pageTitle":"Object.is() - JavaScript | MDN","noIndexing":false}}